snippet.textDisplay:
I thought that the drums would dominate the tabla here. But such is a genius of strings that both of these instruments play in unison to embellish the classical raag Ustadji is singing. Also the piano, violin and the bass are not dominating, just decorating the beautiful jugalbandhi of singing and sitar.
Bravo!
